        <div class="card" style="width: 60rem">
            <h2 class="card-title text-center">About the Website</h2>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>This website is home to a competitive quiz game on object-oriented programming.</p>
                <p>The game puts groups of 2 - 8 players against each other as they answer questions to try to get as many points as they can. After the questions have been asked, the scores for everyone in that game session is displayed</p>
                <br>
                <p>To play the game, you will have to create a new account on the Registration page.</p>
                <p>After signing into the account on the Log-In page, you will have access to the game, and the Leaderboard page, where you can view the scores you have received from all your previous games</p>
                <br>
                <p>To read about what to do for each page, click on the button below</p>

